<h2 style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #333333; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;'>
  Password Reset Successful
</h2>

<p style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  Hi
  {{firstName}},
</p>

<p style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  Your password has been successfully reset. You can now log in to your account using your new
  password.
</p>

{{#if emailWasVerified}}
  <div
    style='background-color: #dbeafe; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 15px; margin: 30px 0;'
  >
    <p style='margin: 0; color: #1e40af; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;'>
      ✅ Email Verified
    </p>
    <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'>
      Your email address has been automatically verified as part of the password reset process. You
      now have full access to all features of your account.
    </p>
  </div>
{{/if}}

<div style='background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0;'>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;'>
    Reset Details:
  </p>
  <ul style='margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'>
    <li>Email: {{email}}</li>
    {{#if resetTime}}<li>Time: {{resetTime}}</li>{{/if}}
    {{#if ipAddress}}<li>IP Address: {{ipAddress}}</li>{{/if}}
  </ul>
</div>

<div
  style='background-color: #fee2e2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; margin: 30px 0;'
>
  <p style='margin: 0; color: #991b1b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;'>
    ⚠️ Wasn't you?
  </p>
  <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'>
    If you didn't reset your password, your account may be compromised. Please:
  </p>
  <ul
    style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'
  >
    <li>Change your password immediately</li>
    <li>Review your recent account activity</li>
    <li>Contact our support team at
      {{#if supportEmail}}<a
          href='mailto:{{supportEmail}}'
          style='color: #ef4444; text-decoration: none;'
        >{{supportEmail}}</a>{{else}}support immediately{{/if}}
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div
  style='background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; margin: 30px 0;'
>
  <p style='margin: 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;'>
    Security Reminder
  </p>
  <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #78350f; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'>
    • All your active sessions have been logged out for security<br />
    • You'll need to log in again on all your devices<br />
    • Use a strong, unique password for your account<br />
    • Consider enabling two-factor authentication if available
  </p>
</div>

<p style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  For your security, we recommend using a password manager to generate and store strong, unique
  passwords for all your accounts.
</p>

<p style='margin: 20px 0 0 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  Best regards,<br />
  {{#if companyName}}The {{companyName}} Team{{else}}The Cotizate Team{{/if}}
</p>